column2: SELECT   ra, dec, z, zErr, extinction_r,   --- some useful imaging parameters   petroMag_r, psfMag_r, psfMagErr_r,   modelMag_u, modelMagErr_u,    modelMag_g, modelMagErr_g,   modelMag_r, modelMagErr_r,    modelMag_i, modelMagErr_i,   modelMag_z, modelMagErr_z INTO mydb.SDSSspecgalsDR8 FROM SpecPhotoAll WHERE   --- add some quality cuts to get rid of obviously bad measurements   AND (petroMag_r > # AND petroMag_r < #)   AND (modelMag_u-modelMag_r) > #   AND (modelMag_u-modelMag_r) < #   AND (modelMag_u > # AND modelMag_u < #)   AND (modelMag_g > # AND modelMag_g < #)   AND (modelMag_r > # AND modelMag_r < #)   AND (modelMag_i > # AND modelMag_i < #)   AND (modelMag_z > # AND modelMag_z < #)   AND (zErr > # AND zErr < #)   AND z > #   --- end of query ---SELECT
